text:
Santa Monica, Calif.-based Tommy Kendall, 51, a retired champion auto racer in the Motorsports Hall of Fame of America and a current television broadcaster, on his 1973 “El Gallo” Oldsmobile Ninety-Eight, as told to A.J. Baime.
